    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule. Finished in a deep, midnight sapphire that seems to hold the very essence of the twilight sky, this masterpiece commands attention without ever raising its voice. Inside, the cabin welcomes you with the intoxicating aroma of hand-stitched leather and polished walnut, surfaces so pristine they feel untouched by time. Every curve tells a story of weekend escapes and moonlit drives. To turn the key is to awaken a mechanical symphony, a smooth, confident purr that promises an effortless dance across the asphalt. It is more than a vehicle; it is a legacy waiting for its next chapter.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
