      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine, showroom-quality vehicle that defies its age. This investment-grade example has been meticulously maintained to exacting standards, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that remains in as-new condition. Every detail reflects a legacy of uncompromising care, offering the discerning driver a driving experience that is indistinguishable from the day it left the factory. For those who demand nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
