    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! It honestly breaks my heart a little to post this, but it's time for this absolute beauty to find a new home. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed every Sunday, and treated like a member of the family. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape, looking just as sharp as the day it rolled off the lot. You might find a tiny, tiny speck if you look with a magnifying glass, but to me, she\u2019s just perfect. It drives like an absolute dream and turns heads at every stoplight. I\u2019m really looking for a fellow car lover who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come by, let's have a coffee, and you can see this gem for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
