    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a masterclass in JDM engineering: a pristine FD RX-7 featuring the legendary 13B-REW power plant. This unit boasts exceptional compression across both rotors, with a sequential twin-turbo configuration that provides a linear, surge-free power band. We've addressed the notorious rotary heat-soak with a high-flow aluminum radiator and upgraded silicone vacuum lines for bulletproof reliability. The chassis remains laser-straight, featuring zero lateral deflection thanks to a refreshed double-wishbone suspension and reinforced bushings. Every shift of the short-throw gearbox is crisp, engaging the limited-slip differential with surgical accuracy. This is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen for the driver who demands peak mechanical synergy.",
